\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 from which it seemed to have come. Just as I had convinced
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 myself that what I believed I had seen was no more than a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 fault of vision, pe\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 rhaps some lingering effect of the drug I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 had been given in the hetman's house, there was a flare of
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 magenta a trifle to the left of the point I had been staring at.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I continued to stand there for a watch or more, rewarded
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 from time to time with these my\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 steries of light. At last, having 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 satisfied myself that they were a great way off and came
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 no nearer, and that they did not appear to change in frequency, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 coming on the average with each five hundredth
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 beat of my heart, I lay down again. And because I wa\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 s then
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 thoroughly awake, I became aware that the ground was shaking, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 very slightly, beneath me.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 When I woke again in the morning it had stopped. I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 watched the horizon diligently for some time as I walked
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 along, but saw nothing disturbing.
\par 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 It had been t\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 wo days since I had eaten, and I was no longer
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 hungry, though I was aware that I did not have my normal
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 strength. Twice that day I came upon little houses falling to
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ruin, and I entered each to look for food. If anything had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 been left, it had been taken lo\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ng before; even the rats were
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 gone. The second house had a well, but some dead thing had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 been thrown down it long ago, and in any case there was no
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 way to reach the stinking water. I went on, wishing for some-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 -thing to drink and also for a better staff th\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 an the succession
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of rotten sticks I had been using. I had learned when I had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 used Terminus Est as a staff in the mountains how much
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 easier it is to walk with one.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 About noon I came upon a path and followed it, and a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 short time afterward heard the sound \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of hoofs. I hid where I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 could look down the road; a moment later a rider crested the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 next hill and flashed past me. From the glimpse I had of him,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 he wore armour somewhat in the fashion of the commanders
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of Abdiesus's dimarchi, but his wind-stiffened cape \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 was green
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 instead of red and his helmet seemed to have a visor like
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the bill of a cap. Whoever he was, he was magnificently
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 mounted: His destrier's mouth was bearded with foam and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 its sides drenched, yet it flew by as though the racing signal
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 had dropped o\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 nly an instant before.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Having encountered one rider on the path, I expected others. 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 There were none. For a long while I walked in tranquillity, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 hearing the calls of birds and seeing many signs of
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 game. Then (to my inexpressible delight) the path forded\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 young stream. I walked up a dozen -strides to a spot where
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 deeper, quieter water flowed over a bed of white gravel. Minnows 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 skittered away from my boots\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 always a sign of good
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 water\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 and it was still cold from the mountain peaks and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 sweet with the memory\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  of snow. I drank and drank again,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and then again, until I could hold no more, then took off my
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 clothes and washed myself, cold though it was. When I had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 finished my bath and dressed and returned to the place
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 where the path crossed the stream, I saw two pu\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 g marks on
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the other side, daintily close together, where the animal had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 crouched to drink. They overlay the hoofprints of the officer's 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 mount, and each was as big as a dinner plate, with no
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 claws showing beyond the soft pads of the toes. Old Midan,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 who h\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ad been my uncle's huntsman when I was the girl-child
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Thecia, had told me once that smilodons drink only after
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 they have gorged themselves, and that when they have
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 gorged and drunk they are not dangerous unless molested. I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 went on.                         \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 The path wound through a wooded valley, then up into a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 saddle between hills. When I was near the highest point, I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 noticed a tree two spans in diameter that had been torn in
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 half (as it. appeared) at about the height of my eyes. The ends
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of both the sta\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 nding stump and the felled trunk were ragged,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 not at all like the smooth chipping of an axe. In the next two
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 or three leagues I walked, there were several score like it.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Judging from the lack of leaves, and in some cases of bark, on-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the fallen parts, and \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the new shoots the stumps had put
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 forth, the damage had been done at least a year ago, and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 perhaps longer.                                   
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 At last the path joined a true road, something I had heard
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of often, but never trodden except in decay. It was m\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 uch like
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the old road the uhlans had been blocking when I had become 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 separated from Dr. Talos, Baldanders, Jolenta, and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Dorcas when we left Nessus, but I was unprepared for the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 cloud of dust that hung about it. No grass grew upon it,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 though it was wider t\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 han most city streets.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I had no choice except to follow it; the trees about it were
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 thick set, and the spaces between them choked with brush.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 At first I was afraid, remembering the burning lances of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 uhlans; still, it seemed probable that the law that\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  prohibited
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the use of roads no longer had force here, or this one would
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 not have seen as much traffic as it clearly had; and when, a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 short time later, I heard voices and the sound of many marching 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 feet behind me, I only moved a pace or two into the trees
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and watched openly while the column passed.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 An officer came first, riding a fine champing blue whose
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 fangs had been left long and set with turquoise to match his
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 bardings and the hilt of his owner's estoc: The men who
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 followed him on foot were antepilan\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 i of the heavy infantry, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 big shouldered and narrow waisted, with sun-bronzed.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 expressionless faces. They carried three-pointed korsekos,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 demilunes, and heavy-headed voulges. This mixture of armaments, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 as well as certain discrepancies among their badges
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 a\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 nd accoutrements, led me to believe that their mora was
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 made up of the remains of earlier formations. If that were so,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the fighting they must have seen had left them phlegmatic.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 They swung along, four thousand or so in all, without excitement, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 reluctance,\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  or any sign of fatigue, careless in their bearing 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 feat not slovenly, and seemed to keep step without
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 thought or effort.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Wagons drawn by grunting, trumpeting trilophodons followed. 
