\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 had been in the mountains, or even in the region about Lake
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Diuturna, so that although t recalled the blanket I had found
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 in t\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 he dead man's pack, I felt no need of it. My task had
