\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "I suppose that he was in love."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "No, that was what was right with him. Every person, you
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 see, is like a plant. There is a beautiful green part, o\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ften with
