\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the plant the strength to climb toward the sun, though they
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 know nothing of it. Suppose that some scythe, whis\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 tling
