\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 stalk."                                                  
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You are saying that evil is good."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "No. I am saying that the things \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 we love in others and
