\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 his chickens. Everyone knows that when chicks are observed
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 to be little cocks they must \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 be caponized. Only one cock is
