\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 grow up,' he said. 'Let them fight, and let me tell you some-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 thing, neighbour. The best and cockiest cock will win, a\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 nd he
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 is the one who will sire many more chicks to swell my flock.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 What's more, his chicks will be the hardiest, and the best
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 suited to throwing off every disease\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 when your chickens are
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 wiped out, you can come to me and I'll sell you some breed-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ing stock \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 at my own price. As for the beaten cocks, my family
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and I can eat them. There's no capon so tender as a cock that
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 has been fought to death, just as the best beef comes from a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 bull that has died in the bull ring and the best venison from a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 stag the hounds h\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ave run all day. Besides, eating capons saps
