\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 were right. But we don't; we even help animals when we can.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Conexa Epicharis used to say we stopped at insects, but then
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 she found one of us\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 I mean a postulant\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 trying to mend a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 butterfly's wing."
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Doesn't it bother yo\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 u that these soldiers have been doing
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 their best to kill Ascians?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Her answer was very far from what I had expected. "As-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 cians are not human."
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 'I\hich\f2 \rquote \loch\f2 ve already told you that the patient next to me is an
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Ascian. You're taking care of him, and as well as yo\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 u take
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 care of us from what I've seen."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "And I've already told you that we take in animals when
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 we can. Don't you know that human beings can lose their
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 humanity?"
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You mean die zoanthropes. I've met some."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Them, of course. They give up their humanity \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 deliberately. 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 There are others who lose theirs without intending to,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 often when they think they are enhancing it, or rising to
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 some state higher than that to which we are born. Still others, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 like the Ascians, have it stripped from them."     
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I thought o\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 f Baldanders, plunging from his castle wall into
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Lake Diutuma. "Surely these ... things deserve our sympathy."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Animals deserve our sympathy. That is why we of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 order care for them. But it isn't murder for a man to kill
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 one."
