\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of the Conciliator, let us say\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 could cure human beings, it
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 might nevertheless fail with those who are not human?"
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You mean the Claw. Close your mouth, please\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 y\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ou make
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 me want to laugh when you leave it open like that, and we're
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 not supposed to when people outside the, order are around."
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You know!"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Your nurse told me. She said you were mad, but in a nice
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 way, and that she didn't think you would ever hurt any\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 one.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Then I asked her about it, and she told. You have the Claw,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and sometimes you can cure the sick and even raise the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 dead."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Do you believe I'm mad?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Still smiling, she nodded.
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Why? Never mind what the Pelerine told you. Have I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 said anything to you \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 tonight to make you think so?"
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Or spellbound, perhaps. It isn't anything you've said at
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 all. Or at least, not much. But you are not just one man."
