\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 In the fading light I could scarcely make them out. I ran
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 my fingers across them. "Only that they are ver\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 y old and were
