\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 keep the best destriers they breed for themselves, but it is tothis port that th\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ey bring the best of those they sell, and there
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the youngest suitor and the angel bought good mounts an
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 filled their saddlebags with gems and gold, and set out for the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 armiger's house that is so remote that no one ever comes
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 there.
\par 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Many a scrape did they\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  have upon the way, and many a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 time bloody the swords that had been washed so often in the
