\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "The youngest suitor dressed himself in the finest of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 clothes he had bought when they had returned to port, and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 soon was at the door of the armiger\hich\f2 \rquote \loch\f2 s daughter.
\par 
\par \tab \loch\af2\dbch\af23\hich\f2 \'93\loch\f2 He found her sitting on a wind\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ow seat, turning the pages
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of one of the old books her mother had carried from her own
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 home and listening to the singing of a lark in a cage. To that
