\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the wind to exercise his wings. Soon he returns to it again,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 wher\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 e there is food for him, clean water, and safety."
\par 
