\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I said, "When one has lived long with danger ..."
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "I understand. I know nothing of war, but much of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 men and women who have seen it."
