\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You were in the chapel giving thanks, then, for your recovery."
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I hesita\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ted. "I had much to say. Chatelaine. That was a
