\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Fighting is a stupid business at best; but there are things to
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 be learned about it, of which the first is that numbers tell
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 only in time. \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 The immediate struggle is always that of an
