\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 In the madness of battle it did so, for it seemed a part of that
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 madness. The frenzied\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  figures were male and female: the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 women had small but pendulous breasts and were half a head
