\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 brilliant, wild eyes, hair clipped nearly to the skull, starved
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 faces, screaming mouths, and prominent\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  teeth.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 We fought free as the cherkajis had; the square had been
