\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 In his convulsions he \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 threw his blazing spear into the air; I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 remember how it twisted against the dark blue sky.
