\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I felt as strong as I ever had in my life and told him so.
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Still, you'\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 d better get a bandage on that leg."
