\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 The savages seemed to have vanished. A new force appeared 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 in their place, on the flank that had now become our
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 front. At fir\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 st I thought they were cavalry on centaurs, creatures 
