\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Our directions of advance were nearly parallel but slowly
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 converged. The dwarfs watched us with what seemed a sullen
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 attention. The tall men did not l\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ook at us at all. At last,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 when our column was no more than a couple of chains from
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 theirs, we halted and turned to face them. With a horror I
