\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 WHEN I REGAINED consciousness, it was the pain in my leg
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 that I felt first. It was pinned beneath the body of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 piebald, and I struggle\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 d to free it almost before I knew who I
