\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Every long story, if it be told truly, will be found to contain 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 all the elements that have contributed to the human
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 drama since the first rude ship reached the strand of Lune:
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 not only noble deeds and te\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 nder emotion, but grotesquerie,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 bathos, and so on. I have striven to set down the unembellished 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 truth here, without the least worry that you, my
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 reader, would find some parts improbable and others insipid;
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and if the mountain war was the scene of high dee\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ds (belonging 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 more to others than to me), and my imprisonment by
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Vodalus and the Ascians a time of horror, and my passage on
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the }{\b\i\dbch\af23 \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Samru}{\dbch\af23 \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  an interlude of tranquillity, then we are come to
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the interval of comedy.
\par 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 We approached that part of the city where the\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  Citadel
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 stands\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2  which is southern but not the southernmost\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 under
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 sail and by day. I watched the sun-gilt eastern bank with
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 great care, and had the captain land me on those slimy steps
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 where I had once swum and fought. I hoped to pass through
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the necropoli\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 s gate and so enter the Citadel through the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 breach in the curtain wall that was near the Matachin Tower;
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 but the gate was closed and locked, and no convenient party
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of volunteers arrived to admit me. Thus I was forced instead
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 to walk many chains along the \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 margin of the necropolis, and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 several more along the curtain wall to the barbican. 
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 There I encountered a numerous guard who carried me
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 before their officer, who, when I told him I was a torturer,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 supposed me to be one of those wretches that, most often \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 at
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the onset of winter, seek to gain admission to the guild. He
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 decided (very properly, had he been correct) to have me
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 whipped; and to prevent it I was forced to break the thumbs
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of two of his men, and then demand while I held him in the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 way called the ki\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 tten and ball that he take me to his superior,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the castellan.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I admit I was somewhat awed at the thought of this official, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 whom I had seldom so much as seen in all the years I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 had been an apprentice in the fortress he commanded. I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 found him an old soldi\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 er, silver-haired and as lame as I. The
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 officer stammered out his accusations while I stood by: I had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 assaulted and insulted (not true) his person, maimed two of
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 his men, and so on. When he had finished, the castellan
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 looked from me to him and back again, \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 dismissed him, and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 offered me a seat.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You are unarmed," he said. His voice was hoarse but soft,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 as though he had strained it shouting commands.
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I admitted that I was.
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "But you have seen fighting, and you have been in the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 jungle north of the mountains,\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  where no battle has been
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 since they turned our flank by crossing the Uroboros."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "That's true," I said. "But how can you know?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "That wound in your thigh came from one of their spears.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I've seen enough to recognize them. The beam flashed up
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 through the m\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 uscle, reflected by the bone. You might have
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 been up a tree and been stuck by a hastarus on the ground, I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 suppose, but the most likely thing is that you were mounted
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and charging infantry. Not a cataphract, or they wouldn't
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 have got you so easily. The demi\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 lances?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Only the light irregulars."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You'll have to tell me about that later, because you're a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 city man from your accent, and they're eclectics and suchlike
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 for the most part. You have a double scar on your foot too,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 white and clean, with the marks hal\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 f a span apart. That was a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 blood bat's bite, and they don't come that large except in the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 true jungle at the waist of the world. How did you get
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 there?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Our flier crashed. I was taken prisoner."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "And escaped?"
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 In a moment more I would have been forced \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 to talk of
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Agia and the green man, and of my journey from the jungle
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 to the mouth of Gyoll, and those were high matters which I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 did not wish to disclose thus casually. Instead of an answer, I
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 pronounced the words of authority applicable to the Citadel
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 its castellan.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Because he was lame, I would have had him remain seated
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 if I could; but he sprang to his feet and saluted, then
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 dropped to his knees to kiss my hand. He was thus, though
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 he could not have known it, the first to pay me homage, a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 distinction\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  that entitles him to a private audience once a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 year\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 an audience he has not yet requested and perhaps
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 never will.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 For me to proceed now, clothed as I was, was impossible.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 The old castellan would have died of a stroke had I demanded it, 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 and he was so con\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 cerned for my safety that any
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 incognito would have been accompanied by at least a platoon 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 of lurking halberdiers. I soon found myself arrayed in
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 lapis lazuli jazerant, cothurni, and a stephane, the whole set
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 off by an ebony baculus and a voluminous damass\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 in cape
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 embroidered with rotting pearls. All these things were indescribably 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ancient, having been taken from a store preserved
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 from the period when the Citadel was the residence of the
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 autarchs.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 Thus in place of entering our tower, as I had intended, in
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 the same cloak in which I had left it, I returned as an unrecognizable 
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 being in ceremonial fancy dress, skeletally thin,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 lame, and hideously scarred. It was with this appearance that
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I entered Master Palaemon's study, and I am certain I must
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 almost have \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 frightened him to death, since he had been told
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 only a few moments before that the Autarch was in the Cit-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 adel and wished to converse with him.
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 He seemed to me to have aged a great deal while I was
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 gone. Perhaps it was simply that I recalled him pot as \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 he was
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 when I was exiled, but as I had seen him in our little class-
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 room when I was a boy. Still, I like to think he was concerned
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 for me, and it is not really so unlikely that he was: I had
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 always been his best pupil and his favourite; it was his vote,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 b\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 eyond doubt, that had countered Master Gurloes's and
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 saved my life; he had given me his sword.  
\par 
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 But whether he had worried much or little, his face seemed
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 more deeply lined than it had been; and his scant hair, which
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 I had thought grey, was now of that \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 yellow hue seen in old
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 ivory. He knelt and kissed my fingers, and was more than a
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 little surprised when I helped him to rise and told him to seat
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 himself behind his table again.
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "You are too kind. Autarch," he said. Then, using an old
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 formula, "Your mercy\hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2  extends from sun to Sun."
\par \tab \hich\af2\dbch\af23\loch\f2 "Do you not recall us?"
